g/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F162013_4314ded96582f0f79cf8818f9028c943.jpg&h=1e92668b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢都講到可有可無，同埋娶個女人返去都係孝順佢阿媽，邊個女人會想比個男人投閒置散樣樣事將個老母掛喺口邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係 馬明應該已經睇透左拍拖同結婚呢d 野 佢根本唔care 有冇女朋友有冇老婆 <br />\n馬明係真正既毒撚性格 自己一個更開心<br />\n唔想煩</blockquote><br />\n同我差唔多性格。<br />\n但我無佢咁靚仔同搵唔到錢"},{"pid":"c74cf99b0c7becf63188678053224d04f29c041a","tid":95543,"uid":3822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:56:52.000Z","msg":"唐詩詠就快到40歲都未搵到真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854143eb81e5e18a064aacb86ea93d3632d9588f","tid":95543,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:58:56.000Z","msg":"唐詩詠可以俾幾多mk仔食"},{"pid":"c8bfed5bffbe62c8b5f9c67891ffc5ac87dd4c95","tid":95543,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:59:41.000Z","msg":"唐詩詠一定係港女"},{"pid":"ac83d3d7c069498d5aa213ec2b121e6a0ef517a1","tid":95543,"uid":19972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote></blockquote><br />\n有幾難明 結咗婚要同佢阿媽住<br />\n有幾多女頂到?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/162013_4314ded96582f0f79cf8818f9028c943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F162013_4314ded96582f0f79cf8818f9028c943.jpg&h=1e92668b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢都講到可有可無，同埋娶個女人返去都係孝順佢阿媽，邊個女人會想比個男人投閒置散樣樣事將個老母掛喺口邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔知點解個男方可以要求個女仔同父母住... 咁女方又要求男方同自己父母住呢?<br />\n4大長老一齊住lor 掉返轉條女d 要求係咁既話 個男仔都覺得惡頂啦"},{"pid":"adda4a392d0b896df423053d62bc78400bd63f3e","tid":95543,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n有幾難明 結咗婚要同佢阿媽住<br />\n有幾多女頂到?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/162013_4314ded96582f0f79cf8818f9028c943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F162013_4314ded96582f0f79cf8818f9028c943.jpg&h=1e92668b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢都講到可有可無，同埋娶個女人返去都係孝順佢阿媽，邊個女人會想比個男人投閒置散樣樣事將個老母掛喺口邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔知點解個男方可以要求個女仔同父母住... 咁女方又要求男方同自己父母住呢?<br />\n4大長老一齊住lor 掉返轉條女d 要求係咁既話 個男仔都覺得惡頂啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢想同父母住唔係問題，大可以同女方商量吓，雖然未必一定肯但起碼有商有量互相尊重，但佢話一定要同父母住就未免太自私，睇埋佢其他條件，根本就唔將女方放在眼內，佢眼中只有父母。"},{"pid":"030fca07236dd520a21a7fd1fa66b56964758dbf","tid":95543,"uid":5419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:21:06.000Z","msg":"唐詩詠命格差<br />\n正宗仆街磁石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54c3439b2bd4e7ca499640b968e6c84a783c1ac","tid":95543,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"今次咕嚕HUNG真係變左咕嚕喇....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb0a1c91e3f89fc00143bd53f1af44ae9f3005e","tid":95543,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:52:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老老豆豆<br />\n洪永城仲有排玩</blockquote><br />\n依家唔係好老, 大把時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重開始做男一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩翠如無選擇佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8c2b83097493f2c2d3aad29848df85d40c3ce3","tid":95543,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一直諗唔明點解馬國明呢類乖仔會冇咩女&quot;hou&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n有幾難明 結咗婚要同佢阿媽住<br />\n有幾多女頂到?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/162013_4314ded96582f0f79cf8818f9028c943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F162013_4314ded96582f0f79cf8818f9028c943.jpg&h=1e92668b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢都講到可有可無，同埋娶個女人返去都係孝順佢阿媽，邊個女人會想比個男人投閒置散樣樣事將個老母掛喺口邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚笑, 邊個幫佢作出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d8be82505978c0743bb00f8931cbac6cfc673c","tid":95543,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日覺得馬明扮戇鳩扮毒食女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黃心穎"},{"pid":"72665d62c143a96a18c554d9802c1b64bb0f7609","tid":95543,"uid":61327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>反而覺得唐詩詠襯唔起洪永城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有少少覺，洪永城細佢兩年，<br />\n樣正常又夠風趣幽默，著起老西都算型棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日覺得唐詩詠個樣好怪 又唔係靚把聲又尖 十足十正統港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e7a2aeddca27262eba62d0cd7cf574814a3604","tid":95543,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:00:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>反而覺得唐詩詠襯唔起洪永城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有少少覺，洪永城細佢兩年，<br />\n樣正常又夠風趣幽默，著起老西都算型棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日覺得唐詩詠個樣好怪 又唔係靚把聲又尖 十足十正統港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我反而好討厭洪永城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d07a1105fff8ca139da5f56532829bf99c4670d","tid":95543,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:01:29.000Z","msg":"馬明去啦吊"},{"pid":"a26675e4a7224b75d31ce14673fbe60fdf1944d6","tid":95543,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/162013_4314ded96582f0f79cf8818f9028c943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F162013_4314ded96582f0f79cf8818f9028c943.jpg&h=1e92668b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢都講到可有可無，同埋娶個女人返去都係孝順佢阿媽，邊個女人會想比個男人投閒置散樣樣事將個老母掛喺口邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔知點解個男方可以要求個女仔同父母住... 咁女方又要求男方同自己父母住呢?<br />\n4大長老一齊住lor 掉返轉條女d 要求係咁既話 個男仔都覺得惡頂啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢想同父母住唔係問題，大可以同女方商量吓，雖然未必一定肯但起碼有商有量互相尊重，但佢話一定要同父母住就未免太自私，睇埋佢其他條件，根本就唔將女方放在眼內，佢眼中只有父母。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有乜好商量 商量完又點 <br />\n最後咪又係男堅持同父母住 女嘅唔想<br />\n咁仲洗乜曬時間商量 直接表明好過"},{"pid":"34803c8a65d8cebc412a972c4840c3198f54e41b","tid":95543,"uid":110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:17:23.000Z","msg":"翻版徐子淇靚好多下話  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3974aa2763b7950df99bdbe730e6a4fe8d99f2","tid":95543,"uid":10620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:25:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔知點解個男方可以要求個女仔同父母住... 咁女方又要求男方同自己父母住呢?<br />\n4大長老一齊住lor 掉返轉條女d 要求係咁既話 個男仔都覺得惡頂啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢想同父母住唔係問題，大可以同女方商量吓，雖然未必一定肯但起碼有商有量互相尊重，但佢話一定要同父母住就未免太自私，睇埋佢其他條件，根本就唔將女方放在眼內，佢眼中只有父母。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有乜好商量 商量完又點 <br />\n最後咪又係男堅持同父母住 女嘅唔想<br />\n咁仲洗乜曬時間商量 直接表明好過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吓原來馬明咁樣嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果佢唔係要求個女嘅同埋佢老豆老母住 我覺得佢真係筍盤黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3febc2f56d035e76c56eee1b949d6e0287dc6dbd","tid":95543,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:31:01.000Z","msg":"條女惡撚到<br />\n同你拍拖就唔可以同異性聯絡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144bc841a53f131247c5407c0ebd07d67aef2ffe","tid":95543,"uid":16511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:42:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>反而覺得唐詩詠襯唔起洪永城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有少少覺，洪永城細佢兩年，<br />\n樣正常又夠風趣幽默，著起老西都算型棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係衰在d 演技麻麻"},{"pid":"61c93c157fbb94a2426ee8b951056683074d9bec","tid":95543,"uid":70943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>反而覺得唐詩詠襯唔起洪永城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br 